title: The Perfect Man
creator: Gabriella Cathleen Maximus
Description: It's a statue of a man holding a phone holding everyone's expectations of what they're looking for in a partner, a "moldable partner" so to speak. The scale is a symbol of the weight of those expectations did to the statue.

title: Complex
creator: Elda Fonseca Leonor Monteiro
Description: The abstract and colorful element of the artwork represents the complexity of each individual

title: Peel off me
creator: Sophie Xelia Gan
Description: I want people to feel what those suffering with OCD especially skin picking feels like, to obsessively look at yourself and with the impulses wanting to peel those cracks, scabs that are healing off in order for yourself to feel “cleaner”, however harming yourself as blood was shed from peeling those imperfections off.

title: The Worlds
creator: JORDAN JUNIO
Description: Representasi pikiran untuk membuat suatu keputusan, di mana kita bisa memilih satu dan tidak akan menjalankan yang lain, membentuk jalan ke masa depan yang telah kita tentukan.

title: Where You Are Enough
creator: Angelina Gunawan
Description: A diorama of a house where a family is welcoming a member and filled with things inside house that is missed by a member

title: Exister, pour nous c’est sentir
creator: Michelle Greta
Description: Two photographs showing two of her sides: the graceful lady by day and the madwoman by night cut up while being surrounded by a pageantry of torn papers; splatters of colors; paragraphs of explicit messages her heart harbors on followed by a plethora of other shenanigans she could find from her family’s house.

title: The Live Facade
creator: Ralph Jeremy Sunarto
Description: The media heavily censored information, carefully selecting and distributing only the content they deemed acceptable for the audience, leaving much of the truth hidden.

title: Time Falls
creator: Artemis Sebastian
Description: Time goes much faster when you don’t notice.

title: A Jellyfish just Woke Up
creator: Kiranya Naddakalila
Description: Fellas have you had a moment where you can't get out of bed for days and all you wanna do is sleep and daydream but when you do get out of bed your hair looks messy as sh- I call it the Jellyfish ways, 'cause not only is your hair messy like jellyfish but you’re also flowing through life without guidance. Bedhead with a jellyfish whimsical concept can blend the natural beauty of jellyfish with the casual, tousled look of bedhead. Just as jellyfish are known for their adaptability in various marine environments, bedhead can symbolize a carefree attitude towards personal appearance and embracing one's natural state after going through that era
